<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">أي س:</span> <span class="c2">(أَيِسَ)</span> مِنْهُ لُغَةٌ فِي يَئِسَ وَبَابُهُمَا فَهِمَ وَ <span class="c2">(آيَسَهُ)</span> مِنْهُ غَيْرُهُ بِالْمَدِّ مِثْلُ <span class="c2">(أَيْأَسَهُ)</span> وَكَذَا <span class="c2">(أَيَّسَهُ)</span> بِتَشْدِيدِ الْيَاءِ <span class="c2">(تَأْيِيسًا)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>